        \r\n                float cellID = hash11(closestSeed);\r\n\r\n               
        return float3(closestDistance, cellID, edgeDist);\r\n            }\r\n           
        \r\n            half4 frag (v2f i) : SV_Target {\r\n                float3
        pos3D = i.vertex.xyz;\r\n                pos3D *= _zoom;\r\n\r\n               
        float4 lookup = float4(pos3D, _Time.y * 0.3);\r\n\r\n                half3
        color = voronoi4D(lookup);\r\n\r\n                return half4(color.rgb,
        1.0);\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            ENDCG\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\u200B"
